\section list Mailing list

There is no mailing list specifically for tracter, but it is covered
by the juicer mailing list.  To join send a message to
juicer-list-request@idiap.ch with the word "subscribe" in the body.
It is <a
href="http://www.gnu.org/software/mailman/index.html">mailman</a>
managed and understands all the usual commands.

